query.esql:
FROM logs-corelight.various*
| WHERE event.dataset == "rdp" and observer.hostname IS NOT NULL and rdp.cookie IS NOT NULL and event.outcome IS NOT NULL
| LIMIT 10000
| STATS  COUNT() by rdp.cookie, event.outcome 
| RENAME rdp.cookie as Connecting_User, event.outcome as auth_success, `COUNT()` as count  
| SORT count DESC
| LIMIT 20
| KEEP Connecting_User, auth_success, count
